Title: Quacking Out for a Hero
Description:
<This duckling has been bubbled so long that it's fallen fast asleep. It quacks softly as it snores.>

<Maybe the ecologists would know how to help it?>
ObjectivesText: Bring the Bubbled Duckling back to the Ecologists' Camp.

Objectives.Text: Bubbled Duckling brought to the Ecologist's Camp
